.Panel
  .Container
    .Container-column
      .Layout-largeMargin
      .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--centerHorizontally
        h1.Heading.Heading--brand.Heading--large
          span> Our
          span.Heading-highlight Services
  .Layout-largeMargin
  .Container
    .Container-column
      .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--centerHorizontally
        .Heading
          | We’ve mastered a set of services based on years of learning and practice.
        .Layout-smallMargin
        .Text
          ' If you’re not sure your problem is within our expertise,
          = mail_to 'core@subvisual.co', 'we should talk', class: 'Link Link--highlight'
          |. If we’re not a perfect match, we’ll recommend you another team that’s a better fit.
  .Layout-defaultMargin
  .Container
    .FramedContainer
      .FramedContainer-cell
        .Layout-defaultMargin
        .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--centerHorizontally
          = partial 'work/product_development.svg'
        .Layout-defaultMargin
        .Heading.Heading--brand
          .Heading-highlight
            | Product Development
        .Layout-smallMargin
        .Text
          | If you want to create a product or take your current one to a new level
        .Layout-smallMargin
        = link_to 'Learn more', '#', class: 'EngagementLink'
        .Layout-largeMargin
      .FramedContainer-cell
        .Layout-defaultMargin
        .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--centerHorizontally
          = partial 'work/consulting.svg'
        .Layout-defaultMargin
        .Heading.Heading--brand
          .Heading-highlight
            | Consulting
        .Layout-smallMargin
        .Text
          | Build your own software following our principles and process
        .Layout-smallMargin
        = link_to 'Learn more', '#', class: 'EngagementLink'
        .Layout-largeMargin
      .FramedContainer-cell
        .Layout-defaultMargin
        .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--centerHorizontally
          = partial 'work/training.svg'
        .Layout-defaultMargin
        .Heading.Heading--brand
          .Heading-highlight
            | Training
        .Layout-smallMargin
        .Text
          | Build your own software following our principles and process
        .Layout-smallMargin
        = link_to 'Learn more', '#', class: 'EngagementLink'
        .Layout-largeMargin
  .Layout-largeMargin
  .Container
    .Container-column
      .ContentFormatter.ContentFormatter--centerHorizontally
        .Heading
          | You can use our project planner to specify your project’s singularities
      .Layout-smallMargin
      = link_to 'Ready to Start', '#', class: 'ButtonPrimary'
  .Layout-largeMargin
